---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About Fix My Furnace | Our Michigan HVAC Story"
  description="Learn how Fix My Furnace was born from frustration with shady contractors and non-transparent pricing. We're Michigan residents connecting you with vetted, honest HVAC professionals."
  keywords="about Fix My Furnace, Michigan HVAC company, transparent pricing, trusted furnace repair, HVAC network Michigan"
>

<!-- HERO SECTION -->
<section class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-red-900 to-gray-900 text-white py-32 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background pattern -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
    <div class="absolute w-full h-full" style="background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, transparent, transparent 35px, rgba(255,255,255,.05) 35px, rgba(255,255,255,.05) 70px);"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl relative z-10 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black mb-6 leading-tight">
      Born From <span class="text-red-400">Frustration.</span><br/>
      Built on <span class="text-yellow-400">Trust.</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
      We got tired of watching Michigan families get burned by shady contractors. So we built something better.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- THE PROBLEM -->
<section class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM8.707 7.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414L8.586 10l-1.293 1.293a1 1 0 101.414 1.414L10 11.414l1.293 1.293a1 1 0 001.414-1.414L11.414 10l1.293-1.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L10 8.586 8.707 7.293z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
            </svg>
            The Old Way
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li>• Wildly different quotes with no explanation</li>
            <li>• Hidden fees appearing after work starts</li>
            <li>• Pressure to "fix it today" before you can think</li>
            <li>• No way to verify if you're being overcharged</li>
            <li>• Shady contractors with no accountability</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-blue-50 rounded-xl p-6 border-2 border-green-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
            </svg>
            The Better Way
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 font-semibold">
            <li>• One honest diagnosis, multiple vetted options</li>
            <li>• Transparent pricing before work begins</li>
            <li>• No pressure — you choose what's right</li>
            <li>• Provider comparison so you can decide</li>
            <li>• Accountability through our network</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
  
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-red-50 to-orange-50 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 border-2 border-red-100 mb-12">
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-800 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            <strong class="text-red-600">It shouldn't be this hard to find honest help.</strong>
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            We're Michigan residents, just like you. We've lived through brutal winters. We've dealt with furnaces that quit at the worst possible time. And we've experienced the frustration of trying to find someone trustworthy to fix them.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            The same story kept repeating: hidden fees, pressure tactics, inflated quotes, and contractors who disappeared after taking your money. Shopping around for prices felt like playing Russian roulette — you never knew if you were getting ripped off or getting quality work.
          </p>
        </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- OUR SOLUTION -->
<section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 via-white to-gray-50">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6">
        So We Built <span class="text-red-600">Fix My Furnace</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
        A better way to get your heating system fixed — with honesty, transparency, and Michigan values.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8 md:p-12 border border-gray-200 mb-12">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">What Makes Us Different</h3>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6.267 3.455a3.066 3.066 0 001.745-.723 3.066 3.066 0 013.976 0 3.066 3.066 0 001.745.723 3.066 3.066 0 012.812 2.812c.051.643.304 1.254.723 1.745a3.066 3.066 0 010 3.976 3.066 3.066 0 00-.723 1.745 3.066 3.066 0 01-2.812 2.812 3.066 3.066 0 00-1.745.723 3.066 3.066 0 01-3.976 0 3.066 3.066 0 00-1.745-.723 3.066 3.066 0 01-2.812-2.812 3.066 3.066 0 00-.723-1.745 3.066 3.066 0 010-3.976 3.066 3.066 0 00.723-1.745 3.066 3.066 0 012.812-2.812zm7.44 5.252a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">We're Your Advocate, Not Just Another Contractor</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              We diagnose your problem honestly, then connect you with vetted providers from our network. You get options, not a sales pitch.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path d="M9 6a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zM17 6a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zM12.93 17c.046-.327.07-.66.07-1a6.97 6.97 0 00-1.5-4.33A5 5 0 0119 16v1h-6.07zM6 11a5 5 0 015 5v1H1v-1a5 5 0 015-5z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">We Built Relationships So You Don't Have To</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              Years of building relationships with parts manufacturers and service providers across Michigan means you benefit from our network, our buying power, and our accountability standards.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Michigan-Based, Michigan-Focused</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              We're not a national franchise. We're Michigan residents who understand what it's like to wake up on a January morning with no heat. We live here, work here, and care about our neighbors.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path d="M10.394 2.08a1 1 0 00-.788 0l-7 3a1 1 0 000 1.84L5.25 8.051a.999.999 0 01.356-.257l4-1.714a1 1 0 11.788 1.838L7.667 9.088l1.94.831a1 1 0 00.787 0l7-3a1 1 0 000-1.838l-7-3zM3.31 9.397L5 10.12v4.102a8.969 8.969 0 00-1.05-.174 1 1 0 01-.89-.89 11.115 11.115 0 01.25-3.762zM9.3 16.573A9.026 9.026 0 007 14.935v-3.957l1.818.78a3 3 0 002.364 0l5.508-2.361a11.026 11.026 0 01.25 3.762 1 1 0 01-.89.89 8.968 8.968 0 00-5.35 2.524 1 1 0 01-1.4 0zM6 18a1 1 0 001-1v-2.065a8.935 8.935 0 00-2-.712V17a1 1 0 001 1z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Decades of HVAC Expertise In-House</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              Our in-house technicians and team have decades of combined HVAC experience. When you call, you're talking to real experts who can answer your questions and guide you to the right solution.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- OUR NETWORK -->
<section class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6">
        One Network. <span class="text-red-600">All of Michigan.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        From the UP to the Ohio border, from Grand Rapids to Detroit — we've built relationships with trusted service providers across the entire state.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-red-50 to-orange-50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center border-2 border-red-100">
        <div class="text-5xl font-black text-red-600 mb-2">100+</div>
        <div class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Vetted Providers</div>
        <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Licensed, insured, and background-checked</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-50 to-yellow-50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center border-2 border-orange-100">
        <div class="text-5xl font-black text-orange-600 mb-2">83</div>
        <div class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Michigan Counties</div>
        <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Complete statewide coverage</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-50 to-green-50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center border-2 border-yellow-100">
        <div class="text-5xl font-black text-green-600 mb-2">24/7</div>
        <div class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Always Available</div>
        <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Emergency service when you need it</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-orange-600 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 text-white text-center">
      <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">We Service All of Michigan</h3>
      <p class="text-xl text-red-100 mb-2">
        <strong>Through Our Network</strong>
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-red-100 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Whether you're in Detroit, Grand Rapids, Ann Arbor, Lansing, Traverse City, the UP, or a small town in between — our network of trusted providers has you covered.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- OUR PROMISE -->
<section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-gray-800 to-red-900 text-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl text-center">
    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-8">
      Our Promise to <span class="text-yellow-400">Michigan Families</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12">
      <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/20">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">✓ Honest Diagnosis</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300">We tell you exactly what's wrong — no upselling, no scare tactics.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/20">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">✓ Transparent Pricing</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300">You'll see clear quotes before any work begins — no hidden fees.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/20">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">✓ Vetted Providers</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300">Every provider in our network is licensed, insured, and accountable.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/20">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">✓ Your Choice</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300">We present options — you decide what's right for your home and budget.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8">
      Because You Deserve Better Than the Old Way of Doing Business
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center">
      <a href="/home-visit" class="bg-yellow-400 text-gray-900 px-10 py-5 rounded-2xl font-bold text-xl hover:bg-yellow-300 transition-all shadow-2xl">
        Get Started — $125 Diagnosis
      </a>
      <a href="tel:+18334948669" class="border-2 border-white text-white px-10 py-5 rounded-2xl font-bold text-xl hover:bg-white/10 transition-all">
        Call (833) FIX-IT-NOW
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- TEAM SECTION -->
<section class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6">
        Meet the <span class="text-red-600">Team</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
        Real Michigan technicians with decades of HVAC expertise — ready to help.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-red-50 to-orange-50 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 border-2 border-red-100">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8">
        <div class="w-48 h-48 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden flex-shrink-0">
          <img src="/group_photo.png" alt="Fix My Furnace Team" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Experienced. Local. Trusted.</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Our in-house team combines decades of hands-on HVAC experience with a genuine commitment to helping Michigan families stay warm. We're not call center operators reading scripts — we're real technicians who've seen it all and know how to fix it.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            When you call Fix My Furnace, you're talking to people who understand furnaces, understand Michigan winters, and understand the frustration of dealing with unreliable contractors. We built this company to be the service we wish existed when we needed help.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FINAL CTA -->
<section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 via-white to-gray-50">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl text-center">
    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6">
      Ready to Experience <span class="text-red-600">the Better Way?</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Join thousands of Michigan families who've discovered honest, transparent HVAC service.
    </p>

    <a href="/home-visit" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-red-600 text-white px-10 py-5 rounded-2xl font-bold text-xl hover:bg-red-700 transition-all shadow-2xl">
      Start With $125 Diagnosis
      <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
      </svg>
    </a>

    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-6">
      Fee credited toward repairs • No obligation • No pressure
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
